> Explain your automation framework:

    - so basically, in my project we have hybrid automation framework using
      python, selenium and pytest

    - we are following the page object model design pattern, where each page
      is maintained as a separate class

    - so it helps into organize our code by separating page elements and test logic.

    - if i talk about the framework structure, we have separate folders for page/models,
       testcases and utilities

    - all the locators and page actions are maintained in page class yaml and page classes
      ,and test logic is written in test files